<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Inconstancy Lamented ƲIT118</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs a̱ holitopa ma!
 Nitak nanta 'k o̱ ʋno ʋt
 Chim il issʋt ai a̱hlichit,
 Ak chi̱ mokofo ka chi̱ cho?

[V2]
 Ʋm anukfila okpulo
 Fitehkahanchi chatuk ʋt
 Katiohmikmak o̱ issʋt
 Ai a̱hlit chullosa chi̱ cho?

[V3]
 Nan ai ashʋche li puta
 Isht nukha̱klot issa li tuk
 Kia, anonti ashʋchit
 Isht sʋlbʋshʋshke, Chisʋs ma!

[V4]
 Katiohmikmak o̱ Chisʋs
 Hatak yoshoba i̱ kana,
 Nana a chim ʋlhtaha ya̱
 Ont isht sa yukpa chi̱ hoh cho?

[V5]
 Chisʋs ma! Chi halanli li,
 Na̱ yukpʋt chiba fohka li;
 Antʋt chi anukcheto li,
 Chi ai okch ya li hoke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs a̱ holitopa ma!</aka>
<hymn_number>118</hymn_number>
</song>